column5: There's some freeroll tournaments going on at PokerStars for Canadians, it's registering right now. Starts a 6:30pm and the second one's at 9:30pm. I'll see you at the final table, SirLargeStax is my user name.
Been on for awhile.I never stood a chance.
Thanks for the "heads up" bud. I actually saw something about it, but forgot it was going on. Might have a serious look now.  Thanks
Well, I'm out of the first one already.  Went all in with A's and lost to a pair of 10's when he caught a 3 of a kind on the turn.
When ever i open up pokerstars it restarts my comp. Anyone have this problem or know how to fix it?
